Today=E2=80=99s Daily Update Interview is with Anduril ( https://www.anduri=
l.com/ ) co-founder and CEO Brian Schimpf ( https://twitter.com/SchimpfBria=
n ). Schimpf went to Cornell, where he competed in the DARPA Grand and Urba=
n Challenges, before joining Palantir and rising to Director of Engineering=
. Then, in 2017, Schimpf founded Anduril with Palmer Luckey, Trae Stephens,=
 Matt Grimm, and Joe Chen, with the mission of =E2=80=9CTransforming US & a=
llied military capabilities with advanced technology.=E2=80=9D

In this interview we talk about Schimpf=E2=80=99s journey and what exactly =
that mission entails. Topics include why now is the time for a software-bas=
ed defense contractor, despite software=E2=80=99s bad fit with the military=
 procurement process; Lattice, Anduril=E2=80=99s software system, and its r=
elation to traditional hardware products; Anduril=E2=80=99s potential as a =
diffuser and conduit for consumer market innovation; and other topics like =
